@startuml 'title' 

!include https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jimbarry0406/pandadoc/main/puml/pandadoc_defaults.puml

autonumber
  
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

  actor Recipient order 1
  participant Printer order 2
  participant Scanner order 3
  participant PandaDoc order 4
  actor DocOwnerSender order 5
  
  Recipient -> PandaDoc : Print Document

  autonumber stop
  PandaDoc --> Printer : Electronic Copy <i>(Unsigned)</i>
  Printer --> Recipient : Physical Copy <i>(Unsigned)</i>
  autonumber resume

  Recipient -[#blue]> Recipient : Sign Physical Copy <&pencil>
  Recipient -> Scanner : Scan Physical Copy

  autonumber stop
  Scanner --> Recipient : Electronic Copy <i>(Signed)</i>
  autonumber resume

  Recipient -> PandaDoc : Upload/Attach Signed Document <&paperclip>

  Recipient -> DocOwnerSender : Manual Notifictaion <&bell>

  DocOwnerSender -[#red]> PandaDoc : Manually Completes Document

@enduml
